sequenceDiagram
    participant CLI as CLI / Scheduler
    participant OR as Orchestrator
    participant DI as Discovery
    participant MI as Mining
    participant FI as Filtering
    participant SC as Scoring
    participant Q as Queue
    participant WK as Worker (Execution)
    participant AN as Analysis
    participant RP as Reporting
    participant DB as Dashboard
    participant ST as Storage/Cache
    participant OB as Observability

    CLI->>OR: start run (scope file)
    OR->>DI: run discovery
    DI-->>OR: discovered hosts/URLs
    OR->>FI: filter & dedupe
    FI-->>OR: filtered candidates
    OR->>MI: mine historical sources (wayback, gau, crawling)
    MI-->>OR: mined endpoints
    OR->>SC: score & prioritize
    SC-->>OR: prioritized tasks
    OR->>Q: enqueue scan tasks
    loop worker pool
        Q->>WK: worker pulls task
        WK->>WK: execute scanner(s)
        WK->>ST: store raw artifacts
        WK->>AN: send raw results
        AN->>AN: analyze & enrich results
        AN->>ST: persist findings
        AN->>RP: notify reporting / trigger report generation
        RP->>DB: send SSE update (dashboard)
    end
    RP->>CLI: deliver final report (optional)
    WK->>OB: emit metrics/logs
    AN->>OB: emit metrics
    RP->>OB: emit metrics
